quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,272,LEJSE ‘ALEJKE HUDAHUM WE LEKINNALL-LLAHE JEHDI MEN JESHA’U WE MA TUNFIKU MIN HAJRIN FELI’ENFUSIKUM WE MA TUNFIKUNE ‘ILLA EBTIGA’E WEXHHI ELLAHI WE MA TUNFIKU MIN HAJRIN JUWEFFE ‘ILEJKUM WE ‘ENTUM LA TUDHLEMUNE
  2,273,LILFUKARA’IL-LEDHINE ‘UHSIRU FI SEBILI ELLAHI LA JESTETI’UNE DERBÆN FIL-’ERDI JEHSEBUHUMUL-XHAHILU ‘EGNIJA’E MINET-TE’AFFUFI TA’RIFUHUM BISIMAHUM LA JES’ELUNE EN-NASE ‘ILHAFÆN WE MA TUNFIKU MIN HAJRIN FE’INNALL-LLAHE BIHI ‘ALIMUN
  2,274,EL-LEDHINE JUNFIKUNE ‘EMWALEHUM BIL-LEJLI WE EN-NEHARI SIRRÆN WE ‘ALANIJETEN FELEHUM ‘EXHRUHUM ‘INDE RABBIHIM WE LA HAWFUN ‘ALEJHIM WE LA HUM JEHZENUNE
  2,275,EL-LEDHINE JE’KULUNE ER-RIBA LA JEKUMUNE ‘ILLA KEMA JEKUMUL-LEDHI JETEHABBETUHU ESH-SHEJTANU MINEL-MESSI DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUM KALU ‘INNEMAL-BEJ’U MITHLU ER-RIBA WE ‘EHELLEL-LAHUL-BEJ’A WE HERREME ER-RIBA FEMEN XHA’EHU MEW’IDHETUN MIN RABBIHI FANTEHA FELEHU
  2,276,JEMHEKU ELLAHU ER-RIBA WE JURBI ES-SEDEKATI WEL-LAHU LA JUHIBBU KULLE KEFFARIN ‘ETHIMIN
  2,277,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI WE ‘EKAMU ES-SELÆTE WE ‘ATEW EZ-ZEKÆTE LEHUM ‘EXHRUHUM ‘INDE RABBIHIM WE LA HAWFUN ‘ALEJHIM WE LA HUM JEHZENUNE
  2,278,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ETTEKU ELLAHE WE DHERU MA BEKIJE MINE ER-RIBA ‘IN KUNTUM MU’UMININE
  2,279,FE’IN LEM TEF’ALU FE’DHENU BIHERBIN MINEL-LAHI WE RESULIHI WE ‘IN TUBTUM FELEKUM RU’USU ‘EMWALIKUM LA TEDHLIMUNE WE LA TUDHLEMUNE
  2,280,WE ‘IN KANE DHU ‘USRETIN FENEDHIRETUN ‘ILA MEJSERETIN WE ‘EN TESEDDEKU HAJRUN LEKUM ‘IN KUNTUM TA’LEMUNE
  2,281,WE ETTEKU JEWMÆN TURXHA’UNE FIHI ‘ILA ELLAHI THUMME TUWEFFA KULLU NEFSIN MA KESEBET WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUNE
  2,282,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IDHA TEDAJENTUM BIDEJNIN ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN FAKTUBUHU WE LIEKTUB BEJNEKUM KATIBUN BIL-’ADLI WE LA JE’BE KATIBUN ‘EN JEKTUBE KEMA ‘ALLEMEHU ELLAHU FELJEKTUB WE LIUMLILIL-LEDHI ‘ALEJHIL-HEKKU WE LIETTEKI ELLAHE REBBEHU WE LA